Date: Tue, 30 Jun 2026 15:36:10 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] =?UTF-8?q?Redesign=20TodayPage=20UI=20to=20match=20?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=EA=B0=99=EC=9D=B4=20=EB=A8=B9=EC=9E=90=20Claude=20Design=20han?=
 =?UTF-8?q?doff?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Warm ivory background (#FAF8F5) and warm border (#EDE8E3) throughout
- Slot cards: flat design with status-colored backgrounds and inline labels
  - open: green (#16A34A / #F0FDF4), closed: blue (#2563EB / #EFF6FF)
  - skip: slate (#94A3B8 / #F8FAFC), 참여중: orange (#FF6B35 / #FFF4EF)
- Replace carousel time picker with preset time chips per slot
  (아침 07:00~09:00, 점심 11:30~13:00, 저녁 17:30~19:30, etc.) + direct input
- Group cards: 18px radius white cards with warm border, no background header
- Add status summary chips at top of each group card
- Member rows: pill-badge status display instead of inline text
- Unset members collapsible with dimmed display
- Pots inside group card: compact inline cards with 🍚 icon
- Create pot button: dashed orange border inside group card
- Date nav arrows: circular button style matching design

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
